        "subject": "LU-4788 lfsck: measure namespace LFSCK performance",
        "message": "LU-4788 lfsck: measure namespace LFSCK performance\n\nMeasure the performance of namespace LFSCK for routine-check\ncases and repairing cases under kinds of DNE configurations.\n\nIt also measures how much the namespace LFSCK will affect the\nperformance of creating small files.\n\nThere are no LFSCK 4 patches for the LFSCK 3 performance test.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 mdtfilesystemtype=ldiskfs mdsfilesystemtype=ldiskfs ostfilesystemtype=ldiskfs envdefinitions=SLOW=yes testlist=lfsck-performance\nSigned-off-by: Fan Yong <fan.yong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9422d19d3c0cf72a7c9a896a6b9399824c8606f3\n"
